{"title_page": "Chandrakant Singh", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2017}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Chandrakant Singh\n| image =\n| caption =\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1974|7|17}}\n| birth_place = [[Indore]], India\n| death_date =\n| death_place =\n| occupation = Director, Producer\n| years_active = 1991\u2013present\n}}\n\n'''Chandrakant Singh''' (born 17 July 1974) is an [[India]]n director and producer who has directed Hindi films such as [[Rama Rama Kya Hai Dramaaa]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/bollywood/features/2008/debutant-director-chandrakant-310108.html |title=Director Chandrakant Singh &#124; Rama Rama Kya Hai Dramaaa &#124; Neha Dhupia &#124; Rajpal Yadav - Oneindia Entertainment |publisher=Entertainment.oneindia.in |date=1 February 2008 |accessdate=10 September 2010}}</ref> and [[Bin Bulaye Baraati]]. ''[[Be Careful (film)|Be Careful]]'', Main Zaroor Aaunga and the most recent film he has directed is Kya Masti Kya Dhoom which will due for release in 2019 .<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.planetbollywood.com/displayArticle.php?id=n090110050359 |title='Be Careful'; Shillpi Sharma Will Arrive This October! - Planet Bollywood News |publisher=Planetbollywood.com |accessdate=10 September 2010}}</ref>\n\n==Background==\nBorn and brought up in Indore, Chandrakant Singh hails from [[Jodhpur]], [[Rajasthan]]. His father was in the transportation business and his mother is a homemaker. His brother Abhay Singh is a film distributor. Chandrakant has a Graduation degree in Science - Biology from Devi Ahiliya University. He also did a 9 months course in scripting and direction from [[New York Film Academy]] in Los Angeles.\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| 1996\u20131997\n| Mr. Uday Shankar Pani documentaries\n| Assistant Director\n|\n|-\n| 1996\u20131997\n| [[Mr. Bechara]]\n| Assistant Director\n|\n|-\n| 1999\n| Aaj Ki Ramayan\n| Director\n|\n|-\n| 1999\u20132002\n